text: Marion Bartoli and Anna-Lena Grönefeld won the doubles title in this edition of the Thailand Open. The 2004 edition was cancelled. ==Seeds== # Magüi Serna / Tamarine Tanasugarn (Quarterfinals) # Marion Bartoli / Anna-Lena Grönefeld (Winners) # Jennifer Hopkins / Mashona Washington (Semifinals) # Tatiana Poutchek / Anastasia Rodionova (Quarterfinals) ==Draw== ==References== * Main and Qualifying Draws * 2005 Tokyo Indooor and Pattaya WTA Singles Results Maria Sharapova & Conchita Martinez, Champions Pattaya Doubles 2005
